{"article_id":"7pNlQ2KLpK2uFiJP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Porn star Stormy Daniels on Monday escalated her legal fight with President Trump ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"arguing in court","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"that Trump 's lawyer defamed her","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"by suggesting","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"she lied about an affair with Trump .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"The actress amended her existing lawsuit against Trump ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"adding his lawyer Michael Cohen as a defendant -","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"a day after her widely viewed 60 Minutes interview","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"in which she provided salacious details about the alleged sexual encounter","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"and claimed","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"she had been physically threatened to keep quiet about Trump by an unknown man .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"Cohen and his lawyers did not immediately respond to a request for comment .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"In addition to broadening the lawsuit","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"to include Cohen ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"the new filing argues","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"that a $ 130,000 payment for her silence days before the election amounted to an illegal campaign contribution .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Daniels ' defamation claim centers on a statement","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"Cohen made in February ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"explaining","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"why he arranged the payment to Daniels .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"he used his own money","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"to `` facilitate '' the payoff","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"and said","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"Trump was not aware of his actions at the time .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"`` Just because something is n't true does n't mean that it ca n't cause you harm or damage , ''","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Cohen said in the statement ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"adding","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"that he would `` always protect Trump . ''","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"In her new filings , Daniels said","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"that statement implied","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"she was lying about the affair","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"and exposed her to `` hatred , contempt , ridicule and shame . ''","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"The White House on Monday denied breaking any campaign-finance laws in the payment to Daniels","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"and also sought to cast doubts about her claim","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"that she was physically threatened to keep quiet about the alleged tryst .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"`` The president does n't believe","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"that any of the claims","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"Ms. Daniels made in the interview last night","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"were accurate , ''","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"White House spokesman Raj Shah told reporters","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"when asked about Daniels ' 60 Minutes appearance .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"`` There 's nothing","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"to corroborate her claim . ''","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Daniels ' updated lawsuit and Shah 's remarks from the White House briefing room mark the latest twist in a legal saga","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"that seems ripped from the pages of a New York tabloid .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"The adult film actress and her attorney Michael Avenatti are waging an aggressive public-relations campaign","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"to invalidate a confidentiality agreement with Trump 's lawyer .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"Cohen ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"known as a fierce defender of Trump from his days as a top Trump Organization attorney ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"also is punching back hard .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Cohen 's lawyer sent a cease-and-desist letter to Avenatti","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"after the interview aired Sunday night ,","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"demanding","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"that Daniels retract `` false and defamatory '' claims","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"she made to 60 Minutes .","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"In the CBS interview , Daniels said","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"she agreed to keep silent about the alleged 2006 sexual relationship with Trump in exchange for a $ 130,000 payment","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"arranged by Cohen","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"because she feared for her safety .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Those fears ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"she said ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"were rooted in a 2011 encounter with an unidentified man","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"who threatened her in a Las Vegas parking lot","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"after she first tried to sell her story to a tabloid magazine","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"and told her to `` Leave Trump alone . ''","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"On Monday , Shah declined to say","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"whether Trump watched the interview .","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"He also said","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"the `` White House did n't engage in any wrongdoing '' in connection with election laws .","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"Trump himself ,","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"who routinely torches his political rivals on Twitter ,","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"has been uncharacteristically silent about Daniels","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"- even after she spilled unflattering details about their alleged encounter on national television .","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"( On 60 Minutes , Daniels said","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"she was n't attracted to Trump","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"and described playfully spanking him with a magazine","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"that featured him on the cover . )","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"Trump 's team has denied the affair , a contention","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"repeated by Shah on Monday .","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"`` The president strongly , clearly and has consistently denied these underlying claims ,","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"and the only person","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"who 's been inconsistent","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"is the one","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"making the claims , ''","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"Watchdog groups also have filed complaints","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"arguing","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"that the $ 130,000 payment to Daniels ,","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"made 11 days before the 2016 presidential election ,","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"likely violated campaign-finance laws","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"that limit the size and source of donations to federal candidates .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"Asked why Daniels was paid to stay quiet before the election","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"if the affair did n't happen ,","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"Shah said :","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"`` False charges are settled out of court all the time ,","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"and this is nothing outside the ordinary . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":195,"left":0,"right":194,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":194,"left":163,"right":193,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":130,"right":162,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":109,"right":129,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":102,"right":108,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":1,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":2,"right":100,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left":3,"right":99,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":108,"left":107,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":103,"right":106,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"